<section id="about" class="py-24 sm:py-32 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="reveal mb-16">
      <p class="text-amber text-sm font-medium tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-3">About</p>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold">
        The <span class="italic text-amber">short</span> version.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-12 md:gap-16">
      <!-- Bio text -->
      <div class="md:col-span-3 space-y-6 text-warm-gray leading-relaxed">
        <p class="reveal text-lg">
          I'm a 28-year-old sales leader and entrepreneur based in Boca Raton, Florida, with a deep fascination
          for what AI can do for the businesses that power our everyday lives. I co-own
          <span class="text-warm-white font-medium">OneWave AI</span>, where I lead sales and business development
          to help small and medium-sized businesses adopt AI solutions that actually make a difference — fewer
          headaches, more growth.
        </p>
        <p class="reveal">
          Before OneWave AI, I built revenue engines from scratch. At Miami Christmas Lights, I closed
          $1.3M in my first four months with zero formal training and grew the sales team from 0 to 7.
          At vivenu, I earned Rookie of the Year by exceeding $1M in annual contract value during my
          first year selling API-first ticketing solutions to enterprises across North America and Europe.
        </p>
        <p class="reveal">
          I'm driven by an entrepreneurial mindset — I see problems as puzzles and markets as playgrounds.
          I thrive in environments where I can wear multiple hats: SDR, AE, strategist, team builder.
          My career has been defined by ramping fast, building processes where none existed, and
          delivering results that set new benchmarks.
        </p>
        <p class="reveal">
          Outside of work, you'll find me on the pickleball court, out on the golf course, casting
          a line somewhere near the water, or hunting down the best local food spot. I'm a foodie
          at heart and believe the best conversations happen over great meals.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Quick facts card -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2 reveal">
        <div class="bg-midnight-light border border-midnight-lighter rounded-2xl p-8 space-y-6 sticky top-28 card-hover">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-warm-white mb-4">Quick Facts</h3>

          <div class="space-y-5">
            <div>
              <span class="text-xs text-warm-gray uppercase tracking-wider">Location</span>
              <p class="text-warm-white mt-1">Boca Raton, FL</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="text-xs text-warm-gray uppercase tracking-wider">Current Role</span>
              <p class="text-warm-white mt-1">Co-Owner, OneWave AI</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="text-xs text-warm-gray uppercase tracking-wider">Education</span>
              <p class="text-warm-white mt-1">BBA Marketing — FAU '19</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="text-xs text-warm-gray uppercase tracking-wider">Focus</span>
              <p class="text-warm-white mt-1">AI for SMBs, Sales Leadership</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="text-xs text-warm-gray uppercase tracking-wider">Interests</span>
              <p class="text-warm-white mt-1">Pickleball, Golf, Fishing, Food</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="pt-4 border-t border-midnight-lighter">
            <a
              href="mailto:parkernewell97@gmail.com"
